"3 pounds orange-flesh sweet potatoes (often labeled","3 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil","2  Fuji apples, peeled and cut into 1-in. chunks","2  Golden Delicious, peeled and cut into 1-in. chunks","2  Granny Smith apples, peeled and cut into 1-in. chunks","1/4 cup maple syrup","  Finely shredded zest of 1 lemon","1 tablespoon fresh lemon juice","1 tablespoon chopped fresh thyme, plus sprigs","  About 1 1/2 tsp. kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper"